# UI patterns (apps/web)

- Font: Inter via `--font-inter` / `font-sans`. No circular `--font-sans: var(--font-sans)`.
- Loading: `AppLoader` or `DataTableSkeleton`. No ad-hoc spinners.
- Lists: `DataTable` + `PaginationBar` (`page`/`size` 10–500). No unbounded `findAll` from UI.
- Empty list CTAs: connector-aware — no installed connectors → Marketplace; connectors exist but list empty → primary create route (e.g. Add Connection).
- Toasts: `notify` from `@/lib/notify`. No `toast` from sonner in feature pages.
- API: `apiFetch` / `logout` from `@/lib/api-client` (credentials included).
- Theme: CSS variables in `globals.css` only. Semantic classes. No manual `dark:` brand overrides.
- Buttons: prefer `success` / `warning` / `danger` / `info` / `pill` for colorful actions.
- Forms: `FieldGroup` + `Field` + shadcn inputs/selects. Settings enums use `Select`, not free text.
- Sensitive settings: Show reveals; Hide remasks locally to `********` (never call reveal again).
- IP whitelist: hide editor when OPEN; labeled rows when RESTRICTED.
- Spacing: `flex` + `gap-*`, not `space-y-*`.
- Compose shadcn (`Card`, `Alert`, `Sheet`, `Table`, `Badge`, `Avatar`) before custom markup.

## Reusable components (prefer these)

- **Critical destructive actions** (revoke, delete, uninstall): use `EmailConfirmDialog` — show subject avatar/name/email; require typing that email before confirm. Never native `window.confirm` for admin-critical ops.
- **In-app docs**: use `DocsShell` for `/docs` — left nested nav + search, right reader pane. Register slugs in `lib/docs/registry.ts`; render via `/docs/[slug]` + `MarkdownDoc` (Mermaid fences via `MermaidBlock`). Link with `DocLink` (truncating pill). Never `fetch` arbitrary paths or enable `rehype-raw`.
- **Error isolation**: wrap new feature page bodies and risky widgets in `ComponentErrorBoundary` so one crash does not blank the whole app. Route-level failures use `app/error.tsx` or segment `error.tsx` (e.g. `app/docs/error.tsx`).
- **Live logs**: use `LiveLogTerminal` + `LogLine` from `@/lib/log-line`; SSE via `useSseLog`. See `.cursor/rules/live-log-streaming.mdc`. Connection tests: `ConnectionTestSheet` + `notifyConnectionTestResult`.
- **Empty list CTAs**: if no installed connectors → Marketplace; if connectors exist but list empty → primary create route (e.g. Add Connection). Do not hardcode “Install a connector first” when connectors are installed.
- **Pagination**: `DataTable` + `PaginationBar`; hide bar when `totalElements === 0`; keep Rows select and Prev/Next on one `items-center` row.
